deactivating the seat sensor?

39:18.824 --> 39:19.891
We can sequence it in.

39:19.925 --> 39:21.059
CHARLIE:
Just did that.

39:21.092 --> 39:22.227
DON:
Yeah, that'll work?

39:22.260 --> 39:25.397
In theory. Airbag will blow
before the timer override.

39:25.431 --> 39:28.099
She'll have two, maybe three
seconds to get out of the car.

39:28.133 --> 39:29.868
All right, I'm going
to go help her.

39:29.901 --> 39:31.036
- What?
- Now, wait. Don, Don! Just...

39:31.069 --> 39:32.704
