all right? I got it.

39:32.738 --> 39:33.705
- What are you doing, Eppes?
- Just relax. Quiet.

39:33.739 --> 39:35.707
- Get out of here!
- All right, listen to me.

39:35.741 --> 39:37.609
- Eppes come on, get outta here.
- Listen to me. Just relax.

39:37.643 --> 39:38.977
Charlie thinks he
can disarm it, okay?

39:39.010 --> 39:40.579
So I'm going to
need you to jump.

39:40.612 --> 39:41.813
I'm gonna help you out. Okay,
you with me?

39:41.847 --> 39:42.814
All right. Yeah, I'm with you.

39:42.848 --> 39:44.182
All right, Charlie.

39:44.215 --> 39:45.917
I'm programming in the time
right now. Just hang on.

39:45.951 --> 39:47.185
(trilling)

39:47.218 --> 39:48.720
Here we go. You ready?

39:48.754 --> 39:49.888
All right, stand by!

39:51.056 --> 39:52.424
Okay.

39:52.458 --> 39:54.092
