39:55.927 --> 39:57.929
(screaming)

39:57.963 --> 39:59.197
Stay back, stay back!

39:59.230 --> 40:00.466
(trilling)

40:00.499 --> 40:01.500
(beep)

40:01.533 --> 40:02.167
It didn't detonate.

40:03.101 --> 40:03.735
Bomb's disarmed.

40:03.769 --> 40:05.937
Congratulations,
Professors.

40:05.971 --> 40:06.938
- You all right?
- You all right?

40:06.972 --> 40:07.873
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

40:07.906 --> 40:08.807
Two arms, two legs,
I'm-I'm good, yeah.

40:08.840 --> 40:10.809
