41:11.202 --> 41:13.204
Yeah, well, we can
change that right now.

41:13.238 --> 41:14.706
There you are, my boy.

41:14.740 --> 41:16.007
All right, well,

41:16.041 --> 41:17.075
to Charlie, who, uh,

41:17.108 --> 41:19.244
seriously pulled a rabbit
out of his hat today.

41:19.277 --> 41:20.946
Wow, well...

41:20.979 --> 41:22.180
Oh, sounds like
you have restored

41:22.213 --> 41:23.615
